%N A203400 Partial sums of A050935.
%H A203400 Reinhard Zumkeller, <a href="/A203400/b203400.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%H A203400 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (2,-1,-1,1).
%F A203400 a(n) = a(n-1) + A050935(n) for n > 1.
%F A203400 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, May 01 2026: (Start)
%F A203400 G.f.: x^3/((1 - x)*(1 - x + x^3)).
%F A203400 a(n) = 2*a(n-1) - a(n-2) - a(n-3) + a(n-4). (End)
%o A203400 (Haskell)
%o A203400 a203400 n = a203400_list !! (n-1)
%o A203400 a203400_list = scanl1 (+) a050935_list
